Mowgli befriends Baloo the bear, Bagheera the panther,
 Chil the vulture, and Hathi the elephant. 
 One day, Hathi takes Mowgli for a ride on his back in order
  to give him a tour of the jungle. Mowgli learns that man
   poses a danger to the jungle and the 
animals after seeing part of the jungle destroyed by fire.